A policeman was airlifted to hospital after he was allegedly shot in the head near a petrol station in Kagiso, on the West Rand, at about 1pm today, March 7, the Krugersdorp News reports.Details of the incident are still unclear, but it is believed three suspects were involved. Police were still on scene to look for the suspects. Caxton News ServiceRead original story on krugersdorpnews.co.za